    {"p": "什么时候……，什么时候……", "e": "Repeating a question word like 什么时候 turns it into 'whenever / whatever': the second clause happens at the same (unspecified) time as the first, e.g. 你什么时候来，我什么时候等你.", "x": "你什么时候有钱，什么时候还我。 — Pay me back whenever you have the money."},
